Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.38,0:00:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know there's an awesome\Ntreasure at the end of this sea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.61,0:00:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And whoever gets it can be King\Nof the Pirates! Isn't that exciting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.18,0:00:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unheard-of adventures are waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.39,0:00:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon voyage! Let that shred of courage grow
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.26,0:00:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught a glimpse of\Nthe tail end to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.90,0:00:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The horizons everyone\Ndreamed of were separate at first
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.68,0:00:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but now they can be seen\Nthrough a single telescope
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.82,0:00:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bitter compass of destiny\Nis leading your heart astray
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.16,0:00:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so turn the wheel in the other direction!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.06,0:01:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon voyage!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.13,0:01:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toss aside your bonds and your past
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.37,0:01:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can surely smile despite that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.38,0:01:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tears shed trying to achieve\Nyour dreams aren't for naught
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.86,0:01:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Precious in my life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.26,0:01:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught a glimpse of\Nthe tail end to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.28,0:01:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,# The impregnable fortress, G8! #
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.78,0:01:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,# Pirates can't come near it! #
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.46,0:02:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,# With its 108 cannons jutting out, #
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.46,0:02:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,# it's a hedgehog that protects the peace! #
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.13,0:02:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,# Our pride, G8! #
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.14,0:02:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, though, I hear our fortress\Nisn't very popular lately within the Navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.51,0:02:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I hear there're\Nsome people who call us
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.51,0:02:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,dim-witted hedgehogs made\Nsoft by peace behind our back...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.18,0:02:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not surprising, since we've had hardly\Nany pirate attacks the past few years.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.52,0:02:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.19,0:02:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't me who said that.\NIt's a rumor! A rumor!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.20,0:02:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsk! What's their problem?!\NPeace is wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.70,0:02:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with peace?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.20,0:02:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,# The impregnable fortress, G8! #
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.18,0:03:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every day is a beautiful day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.20,0:03:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, they really tore up this ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.73,0:03:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll probably take at least a week to fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.20,0:03:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our orders are to fix it in three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.87,0:03:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.87,0:03:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did this ship climb a mountain or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.91,0:03:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's you, Mechao-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.58,0:03:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good way of putting it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.25,0:03:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it'd have to climb a mountain\Nor something to get this wrecked!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.58,0:03:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you know, it might've\Nfallen from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.92,0:03:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It probably got caught around the\Nsea gate when entering the port.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.26,0:03:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that area is very narrow,\Nso it's hard to pass through,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.59,0:03:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even for a navigator who's used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.53,0:03:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's stop joking around\Nand get to work already!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.87,0:03:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.21,0:04:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez... Sailors these days don't\Nhave enough love for their ships...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.26,0:04:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Mechao-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.49,0:04:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A State of Emergency Is Issued!\NA Notorious Pirate Ship Has Infiltrated!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.80,0:04:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got a problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.26,0:04:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It appears that we've been invaded\Nby a huge object from the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.60,0:05:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An invasion from the sky?!\NF-From the sky, you said?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.64,0:05:07.29,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Justice"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.31,0:05:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An unidentified mysterious\Nobject has invaded the base!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.32,0:05:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up! Guard the sea gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.32,0:05:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys go watch the coast!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.99,0:05:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sniper Unit! Move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.66,0:05:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm sleepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.33,0:05:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Close the sea gate!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.15,0:05:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there! 4 o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.66,0:05:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,4 o'clock! All lights on the target!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.34,0:06:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Pirate ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.91,0:06:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pirate flag has... a skull with a straw hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.38,0:06:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The Straw Hat Pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.05,0:06:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.05,0:06:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.72,0:06:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Target the Straw Hat Pirates' ship!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.06,0:06:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did somebody say "Straw Hat"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.74,0:06:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lt. Commander Drake!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.07,0:06:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ship that has invaded our base\Nis the Straw Hat Pirates' ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.41,0:06:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat, you say?!\NWhere's Commander Jonathan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.05,0:06:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... we can't find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.72,0:06:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, that man's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.72,0:07:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be damned... To think that\Nsomeone invaded from the sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.41,0:07:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Resistance is futile! We have\Nyou completely surrounded!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.35,0:07:31.35,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Full of Power!"\N"Carbohydrates!"\N"Navy Dining Hall"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.12,0:07:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think it's been pretty noisy outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.46,0:07:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I wonder if there're\Nintruders or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.46,0:07:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.80,0:07:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No chit-chatting!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.80,0:07:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! We have to prepare\Nmeals for 1,000 people!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.41,0:07:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In two hours, a bunch of boys\Nfrom the night shift will show up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.78,0:07:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no time for fooling around!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.45,0:08:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--But...\N--The siren from earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.79,0:08:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, lads!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.46,0:08:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The day this fortress falls\Nis the day the world falls.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.79,0:08:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, when Jessica-sama\Nblows up, she's a lot scarier than...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.80,0:08:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jessica-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.14,0:08:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.30,0:08:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander! Where have you been?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.48,0:08:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't catch anything today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.51,0:08:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.52,0:08:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I had a large catch yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.68,0:08:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not talking about that!\NCommander, if you're always absent...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.86,0:08:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the big deal? Night fishing\Nisn't necessarily a waste, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.53,0:08:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander, I have a report!\NAccording to the watchmen,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.80,0:08:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as well as the maintenance men inside\Nthe dock who saw the ship close by...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.14,0:08:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-According to them...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.14,0:08:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.47,0:08:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spit it out already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.31,0:09:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... well... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.85,0:09:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say they saw ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.52,0:09:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, something\Nsuddenly fell from the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.52,0:09:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A hairy monster appeared.\NIt jumped and then disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.19,0:09:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hands... Hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.86,0:09:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about hands?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.53,0:09:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hands grew out from my body, and the\Nnext moment, everything went black!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.53,0:09:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right... they were a girl's soft hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.54,0:09:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gotta be...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.54,0:09:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A ghost ship!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.88,0:09:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Don't be ridiculous!\N--Yes, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.54,0:09:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without doubt, that is the Straw Hats' ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.58,0:09:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way it's a ghost ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.92,0:09:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover, of all things,\Nto say that it fell from the sky?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.92,0:09:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... the part about it coming\Nfrom the sky, at least, is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.59,0:09:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you that it isn't a waste, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.27,0:10:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Lt. Commander?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.67,0:10:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.00,0:10:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A ghost ship, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.68,0:10:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It smells good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.82,0:10:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander! I found\Nthese in one of the rooms!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.00,0:11:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ingots and a crown... Those are quite old.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.33,0:11:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They must've stolen them\Nfrom some ancient ruins.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.00,0:11:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Send them to the forensics lab!\N--Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.67,0:11:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, let's explore inside, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.55,0:11:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chirps?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.72,0:11:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the one. It's just an ordinary\NSouth Bird. There's nothing to fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.22,0:11:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--South Bird?\N--Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.99,0:11:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a funny bird valued highly by old-time\Nsailors because they always point south.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.54,0:11:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.41,0:11:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.41,0:11:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So they're surprisingly violent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.06,0:12:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're well maintained.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.90,0:12:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Medical books and history books... huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.07,0:12:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess these ghosts study a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.57,0:12:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ghosts again? How ridiculous...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.11,0:12:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for your hard work. Continue\Nthe investigation of this ghost ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.79,0:12:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ghost ship, he says?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.96,0:12:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Got that?\N--Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.13,0:12:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears that that ship\Nstopped by Jaya quite recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.14,0:12:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--The coffee was tasty, wasn't it?\N--Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.74,0:12:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The color and smell of the\Ncoffee left on the deck...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.41,0:12:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was definitely Jaya Coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.74,0:12:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you've got the courage to drink\Nit without investigating it well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.58,0:12:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.12,0:13:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that South Bird... That's a bird\Nthat inhabits the jungles of Jaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.12,0:13:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know? A legend of gold\Nremains deeply entrenched there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.63,0:13:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander, then that ship is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.13,0:13:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know about its crew's whereabouts,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.13,0:13:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's certain that it came from Jaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.13,0:13:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not some ghost ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.80,0:13:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! I've seen that ship twice.\NIt's the Straw Hats' ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.14,0:13:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you, yourself, called it a\Nghost ship earlier, Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.14,0:13:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have fresh recruits\Nand prisoners at this fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.81,0:13:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we tell everyone about\Nthe Straw Hats' invasion
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.42,0:13:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,without knowing their true purpose,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.79,0:13:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it'll only cause confusion\Nwithin the fortress, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.86,0:13:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's just keep calling\Nit a ghost ship for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.86,0:13:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With all due respect, Commander,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.66,0:13:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we should organize a special\Ninvestigation unit right away
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.20,0:13:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and search for them as soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.53,0:13:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please assign it to my unit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.13,0:13:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Now, don't be so hasty.\N--But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.47,0:13:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Building up our defense is the priority now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.47,0:13:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You go reinforce security at the coast\Nas well as around the sea gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.81,0:13:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.98,0:14:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You go reinforce security at the\Nammunition bunker, detention facilities
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.81,0:14:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the major passageways. I'll also\Ngrant you authority to manage personnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.52,0:14:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.52,0:14:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You look dissatisfied, Lt. Commander.\N--No, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.19,0:14:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The night is still long.\NThey probably can't move around much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.86,0:14:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that goes for us, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.86,0:14:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait until morning, then take your unit
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.20,0:14:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and thoroughly investigate\Nplaces where people gather.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.87,0:14:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Places where people gather, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.67,0:14:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.20,0:14:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to find green insects since\Nthey live in green grassy places.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.21,0:14:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the Straw Hats were to wear our uniforms...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.88,0:14:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that I don't trust my men's abilities,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.92,0:14:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's very possible that they'll\Ntake some of our uniforms.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.59,0:14:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates are like stray dogs...\NThey're always hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.19,0:14:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you start by checking\Nthe dining hall once morning comes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.86,0:14:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.87,0:15:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did everyone go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.54,0:15:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.75,0:15:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.25,0:15:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good thing we've got a waver.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.93,0:15:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Security is tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.94,0:15:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd better get out of here right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.82,0:15:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me! This is...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.93,0:15:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well... We've fallen\Nto a troublesome place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.93,0:16:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Nami-san and Robin-chan\Nwere able to escape okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.60,0:16:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What's the matter?!\N--Well, I saw some sort of light in the tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.61,0:16:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were probably seeing things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.32,0:16:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even smoke in peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.00,0:16:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beef, pork, chicken, beef, fish, pork...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.01,0:16:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meat! Meat! Meat!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.28,0:16:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how I look at it, I haven't\Neaten since we left the sky island!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.86,0:17:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that didn't help.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.16,0:17:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Chopper were here, he would've\Ncaught the smell of food for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.00,0:17:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Found them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.00,0:17:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn... We can't even get\Nclose to the Merry like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.34,0:17:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oreja Fleurs!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.68,0:17:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all that, we couldn't find\Neven a single crewmember.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.05,0:17:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even worse, the maintenance guys\Nsaid they saw monsters, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.99,0:17:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, and the Commander clearly\Nadmitted that this is a ghost ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.39,0:17:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How mean... asking us to\Nwatch a creepy ship like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.17,0:17:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Apparently, the Navy thinks\Nthat the Merry is a ghost ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.20,0:17:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A ghost ship?! How rude! I'm gonna sue!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.68,0:17:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's better for us, as well as for\Nthe Merry, if they think that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.52,0:18:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can buy time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.39,0:18:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I know that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.39,0:18:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it! They must've stolen\Ncursed gold from some ruins!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.39,0:18:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out! I touched that gold...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.07,0:18:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gh-Ghost!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.07,0:18:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat Luffy and Pirate Hunter Zoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.61,0:18:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can probably assume that\Nthe woman with countless hands
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.71,0:18:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the hairy monster\Nare also part of the group.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.08,0:18:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, there're seven of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.75,0:18:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Among them are...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.45,0:18:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A skilled cook...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.45,0:18:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A knowledgeable ship's doctor...\NThere may be a historian as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.79,0:18:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard a suspicious noise!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.23,0:18:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.07,0:18:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what's going on! How do\Nthese convoluted hallways work?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.41,0:19:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trapped! What am I gonna do?!\NWhat am I gonna do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.18,0:19:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I gonna do?!\NWhat the heck should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.13,0:19:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's downstairs!\N--Okay, got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.47,0:19:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.48,0:19:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now... where should I head?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.54,0:20:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I thought...\NIt's surrounded by land in all directions.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.88,0:20:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean we fell on a\Nhuge lake with no way out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.93,0:20:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, obtaining the information\Nwe need to escape is our top priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.27,0:20:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's be resolved... Long-nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.60,0:20:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.27,0:21:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just my imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.01,0:21:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot! He's got no sense of tension!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.61,0:21:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I don't know is their purpose.\NWhat on earth did they come here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.36,0:21:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, at any rate, my fortress\Nis no laughing matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.31,0:21:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and get moving towards the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.65,0:22:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's move ahead, pursuing our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.50,0:22:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the answers are right here, pouring out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.51,0:22:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rush forth, rush forth,\Non the road opened before us
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.68,0:22:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's keep moving forward! We can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.25,0:22:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't give in, we won't give in,\Neven if the obstacle is big
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.46,0:22:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing to be scared of,\Nwe can overcome it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.38,0:22:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of all places, this is a Navy fortress?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.35,0:23:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starving!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.49,0:23:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't do anything until\Nwe know the entire picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.55,0:23:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starving!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.72,0:23:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see your cook's spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.06,0:23:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you talking to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.39,0:23:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I'm starving!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.73,0:23:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to the fortress of Navarone!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.73,0:23:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you talking to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.16,0:23:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.56,0:23:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Sanji the Cook! Proving His\NMerit at the Navy Dining Hall!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.73,0:23:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
